---
title: Creamy Bacon, Leek & Veggie Risoni with Herby Roasted Pumpkin & Parmesan
description: What’s going into the risoni today? A little bit of leek and bacon, a heap of roasted pumpkin, a touch of capsicum for that delicious hint of smokiness
and finally a sprinkling of herb seasoning. It’s a perfect concoction of flavour, texture and pure yumminess.

